PALMING: Concealing small objects by hand

Category: Rogue
Base skill: 20% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Sleight of hand: concealing a small object in your palm without
anyone noticing, whether you are lifting something, planting
something, or just making an item disappear from view. A building
block skill for card cheats, pickpockets, and stage magicians alike.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, cardsharp, pick pockets
